  "texts": [
    "We evaluate our models on two widely used datasets, CoNaLa and DJANGO, to demonstrate their performance and capabilities.",
    "Our first model, RoBERTaMarian, integrates the Distil-ROBERTa pre-trained model as the encoder and the Marian decoder.",
    "It achieves impressive performance on both datasets, particularly on DJANGO, where it attains a superior BLEU score of 88.91, an exact match accuracy of 77.95%, Sacre-BLEU of 74.08, and a ROUGE score of 92.76.",
    "These results demonstrate the model's proficiency in generating high-quality code solutions that accurately match humangenerated references.",
    "The second model, BERTMarian, utilizes the DistilBERT encoder and Marian decoder."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}